---
import '../styles/global.css';
import content from '../content/siteContent.json';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const page = content.pages.dcSmart;
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="description" content={page.hero.intro} />
		<title>{page.meta.title} - DC Management</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<section class="relative" style="background:#334355;">
			<Nav currentPage="propuesta" />

			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 py-20">
				<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
							<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold italic text-white/20 tracking-wide">DC SMART</h1>
						</div>
						<p class="text-white/80 text-lg">{page.hero.intro}</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-center">
						<img src="/images/logos/gif-logo.gif" alt="DC Smart Logo" class="w-72 md:w-96 h-auto" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<main>
			<!-- Dashboard Preview -->
			<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #334355, #1a2535);">
				<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 relative z-10">
					<!-- Dashboard -->
					<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl mb-20">
						<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-[#c1b387]/30 shadow-2xl shadow-[#c1b387]/10">
							<img src="/images/dc smart/dcsmart hero image.png" alt="DC Smart Dashboard" class="w-full" />
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Cards con bordes dorados -->
					<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-6">
						<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#c1b387]/20 to-[#c1b387]/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/30 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#c1b387]/50 transition-all duration-300">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Herramientas Propias</h3>
							<p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">{page.tools.body}</p>
							{page.tools.ctaHref && page.tools.ctaLabel && (
								<a href={page.tools.ctaHref} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block mt-4 px-6 py-2 bg-[#c1b387]/20 border border-[#c1b387]/40 rounded-full text-[#c1b387] hover:bg-[#c1b387]/30 transition-colors">
									{page.tools.ctaLabel}
								</a>
							)}
						</div>

						<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#c1b387]/40 transition-all duration-300">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Mejora Continua</h3>
							<p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">Se debe realizar un monitoreo constante del desempeño del negocio y la plataforma, identificando oportunidades para mejoras estratégicas y funcionales.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="col-span-12 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#c1b387]/40 transition-all duration-300">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">{page.deliverables.title}</h3>
							<p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">Los dashboards y reportes constituyen entregables periódicos cruciales para la gestión organizacional. Mientras que los reportes estructuran la información para identificar tendencias, los dashboards transforman datos complejos en visualizaciones dinámicas e interactivas.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/20 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-[#c1b387]/40 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#c1b387]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#c1b387]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Auditorías</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Punto de inicio esencial para impulsar el siguiente paso. Ofrecemos perspectivas valiosas para evaluar el desempeño e identificar áreas de mejora.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/20 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-[#c1b387]/40 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#c1b387]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#c1b387]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Procesos</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Identificamos los procesos que necesitan optimización. Esta etapa es crucial para mejorar la eficiencia y sostenibilidad de la empresa.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#c1b387]/20 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-[#c1b387]/40 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#c1b387]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#c1b387]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Información</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">La gestión eficaz de la información nos permite convertir datos en conocimiento accesible para facilitar decisiones estratégicas.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
